1. Contexto
## Credit Risk Analysis – Exploratory Analysis
Objective: Identify customers with outstanding debt and payment delays.

2. Carga de datos
import pandas as pd
df = pd.read_csv("../data/credit_transactions.csv")
df.head()

3. Validaciones
df.info()
df.isnull().sum()

4. Métricas clave
df["outstanding_debt"] = df["total_amount"] - df["paid_amount"]
df.groupby("customer_id").agg({
    "total_amount": "sum",
    "paid_amount": "sum",
    "outstanding_debt": "sum",
    "days_past_due": "mean"
}).reset_index()

5. Insight escrito (CLAVE)
Customers C003 and C008 show high outstanding debt and high average days past due,
indicating elevated credit risk.
